                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-256-18560204 t18560204-256-punishment-35"></join>Confined Eighteen Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">BOWYER</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18560204-256-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
